fields.description:
External Url not being opened.

1.Package and deploy KS.And open on mobile web browser.
2. Navigate to BaseUI>Views>WebViews>External Url

Expected Result:
2. Google web Page must get open.

Actual Result:
2. Nothing happens. Google web Page does not gets open.

Not a regression as issue occurs in 3.2.0.GA also.
fields.summary: MobileWeb: KitchenSink: WebView could not open the external url link
